                            <comment id="14270909" author="varunthacker" created="Fri, 9 Jan 2015 11:31:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=erickerickson&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;erickerickson&quot;&gt;erickerickson&lt;/a&gt; ,&lt;/p&gt;

