                            <comment id="14271113" author="arafalov" created="Fri, 9 Jan 2015 15:15:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think that whole section refers to the stuff that no longer ships with Solr. I don&apos;t know as of when the shipping it stopped.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14271636" author="hossman" created="Fri, 9 Jan 2015 18:13:22 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;I think that whole section refers to the stuff that no longer ships with Solr. I don&apos;t know as of when the shipping it stopped.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

